":464703,"uid":22638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"輕輕力咬唔係代表中意你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60aea277ff80131f1507fc17f08d1680d692ff2c","tid":464703,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>輕輕力咬唔係代表中意你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一咬埋來就覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d174fcbdadbfd80f1e2e6683058db63ca81b9952","tid":464703,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"我果啲以前喝一喝佢<br />\n佢就停<br />\n<br />\n不過我啲貓好似唔會咬唔會抓人<br />\n唔多覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都無專登教<br />\n除非玩得興奮果陣先唔覺意咬到<br />\n之後即放口<br />\n<br />\n我有六隻貓"},{"pid":"5d27fb4b592409fb60c31b4294729eb8768a1f9e","tid":464703,"uid":8048,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我果啲以前喝一喝佢<br />\n佢就停<br />\n<br />\n不過我啲貓好似唔會咬唔會抓人<br />\n唔多覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都無專登教<br />\n除非玩得興奮果陣先唔覺意咬到<br />\n之後即放口<br />\n<br />\n我有六隻貓</blockquote><br />\n有六隻互咬洗撚咬你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c16aab2853139fc6c14d06c25a1a7071bafa14","tid":464703,"uid":47433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:26:33.000Z","msg":"我隻又係成日撲咬我，有時摸下佢仲用兩隻手攬住我嚟咬，咬完又lam番我，都唔知佢愛我定憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家佢一咬我我就大聲叫，嚇到佢呆一呆，睇下日子有功可唔可以教到佢唔咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c2a3764efda20bf07ce948f50d5a384b8c08be","tid":464703,"uid":766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T20:28:58.000Z","msg":"我一擰轉面就咬我背脊<br />\n之後就望住我扮無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11066861be8b33b093f48019ccc6c7eb4de52c2","tid":464703,"uid":6962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"咬返佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前佢一mak大口就將佢隻手伸入佢口入面比佢咬佢都唔識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一咬就彈佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f15e9879b58c53b12034b285806d4a0745f671","tid":464703,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T16:34:52.000Z","msg":"幾大？慣左唔會教得到<br />\n等佢慢慢大個左定性會咬少左"},{"pid":"4b78ba5a9a78c9df4dfed5159d3c359189ae2e32","tid":464703,"uid":115698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T17:58:23.000Z","msg":"係咪你成日用手同佢玩？所以佢以為你隻手係玩具，認為你隻手咬得？"},{"pid":"8aa1df2eff602b9b9e602b8a48b0163a5afc2e91","tid":464703,"uid":156188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾大？慣左唔會教得到<br />\n等佢慢慢大個左定性會咬少左</blockquote><br />\n點解我唔覺嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5517b87bd4d0cdc0ccb14424d95b5a08090cfe5a","tid":464703,"uid":54345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻又係成日撲咬我，有時摸下佢仲用兩隻手攬住我嚟咬，咬完又lam番我，都唔知佢愛我定憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家佢一咬我我就大聲叫，嚇到佢呆一呆，睇下日子有功可唔可以教到佢唔咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好痛呀<br />\n已經成日鬧佢"},{"pid":"76818d162e75bcdb8e9f03f2a612f252e59cd0e6","tid":464703,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻又係成日撲咬我，有時摸下佢仲用兩隻手攬住我嚟咬，咬完又lam番我，都唔知佢愛我定憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家佢一咬我我就大聲叫，嚇到佢呆一呆，睇下日子有功可唔可以教到佢唔咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻狗都係咁 我懷疑係佢細個係寵物店困係D貓隔離 以為自己係貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e540bee6867b8a028ef2f874285fc53ded6c6de4","tid":464703,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我隻又係成日撲咬我，有時摸下佢仲用兩隻手攬住我嚟咬，咬完又lam番我，都唔知佢愛我定憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家佢一咬我我就大聲叫，嚇到佢呆一呆，睇下日子有功可唔可以教到佢唔咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻狗都係咁 我懷疑係佢細個係寵物店困係D貓隔離 以為自己係貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓性既狗會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3187286b0ecbf405bb3231ca3613c23a01c152f8","tid":464703,"uid":121479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"唔知點解我隻貓一聞到我格甩底，就會大大力咬我膊頭。 我又成日皂液洗格甩底，係咪唔中意隻味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bee248ec455121f075988bc48a900294625b56b","tid":464703,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我隻又係成日撲咬我，有時摸下佢仲用兩隻手攬住我嚟咬，咬完又lam番我，都唔知佢愛我定憎我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家佢一咬我我就大聲叫，嚇到佢呆一呆，睇下日子有功可唔可以教到佢唔咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻狗都係咁 我懷疑係佢細個係寵物店困係D貓隔離 以為自己係貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n貓性既狗會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未養過貓唔知係咪真係似<br />\n但係你上面講既<br />\n「成日撲咬我，有時摸下佢仲用兩隻手攬住我嚟咬，咬完又lam番我」就日日發生<br />\n<br />\n有時D行為見到其他巴打講貓覺得似<br />\n例如朝朝起身都俾佢用爪爪醒<br />\n想R痕就用爪爪我隻手 當你奴隸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec538aa55ecc901c7051f8a01538df25e6334014","tid":464703,"uid":82641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"咬完又lam番 即係佢同你玩"}]}